stu_tags: SKIP CLASS? YOU WON\'T PASS.  TOUGH GRADER
comments: I hated this class. There\'s not really any homework. Just outlines & exams. He does listening exams that are kinda hard. You have to learn the names of foreign songs and where they\'re from. Hard to learn the names. The outlines are long papers you have to type up. Instrument ID\'s and cultural questions. Not a fun class. And an essay.

tag_professor: Tough Grader (1)  Skip class? You won\'t pass. (1)
comments: *HONORS SECTION* The class is pretty boring... He teaches form slides but doesn\'t post them online, so I would go to class. Each unit has an outline that MUST be done. The tests are all LISTENING EXAMS. You have to memorize the songs and the countries for the tests. There is a day where you get to play the instruments, and it is fun!

tag_professor: Tough Grader (1)  Skip class? You won\'t pass. (1)
comments: He is the best teacher I have ever had or will ever have. He should be somewhere better than this school, but no one wants to pay him (or can afford) what he is truly worth. If you have the privilege to take one of his classes, be a sponge and soak up as much as you can; he will teach not only the subject, but about life. Highly recommend!!
